    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>mooli slaw mix</strong> and <strong>rice vinegar</strong> to a large bowl with 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and set aside – this is your <strong>quick-pickled mooli slaw</strong></p>",
