    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and grate your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>grated garlic</strong>, <strong>five-spice mix</strong>, <strong>hoisin sauce</strong>, <strong>honey </strong>and <strong>soy sauce </strong>in a bowl</p><p>Add 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp] </span>[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and stir everything together – this is your <strong>char siu-style sauce</strong></p>",
