    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the fries are nearly done, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Drain, then add your <strong>jumbo prawns</strong> to a large bowl with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp] </span><strong>flour</strong> and mix together until the prawns are fully coated</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated jumbo prawns </strong>to the pan and cook for an initial 4-5 min or until golden</p>",
      "order": 5,
