    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the prawns are golden, add the <strong>char siu-style sauce </strong>to the pan and cook for a further 3-4 min or until the sauce has thickened and the prawns are cooked through – these are your <strong>char siu-style jumbo prawns</strong></p>",
